title: Bug 116609 [Regression] Color orange doesn't work.
description: Bug 116609 [Regression] Color orange doesn't work. Description: Color orange doesn't work.
OB: When previewing the report, the color orange is not displaying correctly.
EB: The expected behavior is that the color orange should be displayed correctly when previewing the report.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert a report item. 2. Set the color or background color to orange. 3. Preview the report to see that the orange color is not displayed correctly.
